## revalidatePath Patterns

```typescript
// Specific page
revalidatePath('/dashboard/orders')

// Dynamic route — all variants
revalidatePath('/orders/[id]', 'page')

// Entire layout (all pages under /dashboard)
revalidatePath('/dashboard', 'layout')

// When to call:
// After INSERT → revalidate list page
// After UPDATE → revalidate detail page + list page
// After DELETE → revalidate list page + redirect away from deleted item
```

